    • LEVEL_1

      private static final Point LEVEL_1
      Each point here represents one of the clickable buttons that map to different levels on the Overworld menu. The point is the top-right coordinate of each button. all points were calculated on paper arbitrary points that look good on screen divide by 1.75f because that is the default scale, then multiple by scale
